# 🩺 AI Health Chatbot

An intelligent, GPT-powered health assistant built with Streamlit. It responds to user symptoms with curated wellness advice, nutritional tips, home remedies, and language translations.

## ✨ Features

- 💬 Chat-style interface with user/bot bubbles (streamlit-chat)
- 🧠 GPT-2 based fallback advice for unmatched queries (Hugging Face)
- 🌿 Curated home remedies for 15+ health conditions
- 📗 Hindi translation using Deep Translator
- 📈 Daily health chart (water, sleep, steps)
- 📋 FAQ search from a Pandas dataframe
- 🎨 Clean and emoji-rich Streamlit UI

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python
- Streamlit
- Transformers + Torch (for GPT-2)
- Streamlit Chat
- Deep Translator
- Pandas + Matplotlib


🚀 Run Locally
To launch the chatbot on your system:

bash
streamlit run health_chatbot.py

✅ This assumes:

Python is installed

All dependencies are set up (via requirements.txt)

You’re in the project folder in terminal

To install the dependencies beforehand:

bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

## 🛡️ Disclaimer

This chatbot is for educational use only and does not replace advice from licensed healthcare professionals.
